  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Sportvida CyberDash</strong> is a <strong>VR running game</strong> that delivers both stress relief and thrilling challenges. Set in a high-speed, futuristic world of light and technology, you’ll embark on an intense adventure where <strong>sprinting, dodging, and smashing obstacles</strong> offer an unparalleled sense of release.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136070/extras/835277f48f4abddbb4fde8ed09b89e20.poster.avif?t=1769591396\" width=702 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136070/extras/835277f48f4abddbb4fde8ed09b89e20.webm?t=1769591396\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136070/extras/835277f48f4abddbb4fde8ed09b89e20.mp4?t=1769591396\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > In this breathtaking and luminous future world, your mission is to race to the finish line in the shortest time possible, breaking through anything that stands in your way. The game’s stunning visual effects, combined with its high-energy soundscape, immerse you in a sensation of speed and power like never before. Sportvida CyberDash is not just about exercise—it’s an exhilarating experience that lets you challenge yourself while unwinding in a fast-paced, visually stunning environment. <strong>Whether you're a fitness enthusiast or simply seeking stress relief, this game will help you find your rhythm and rediscover joy in movement.</strong>  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136070/extras/54c9436540d69b9ffa2373314cee2f5b.avif?t=1769591396\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136070/extras_big/54c9436540d69b9ffa2373314cee2f5b.avif?t=1769591396 width=800 height=125 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>💥3 Unique Game Modes</strong>:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Race Mode</strong> – Pure running with no speed limits and no obstacles—push yourself to the max and challenge your top speed!<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136070/extras/94451b228819058279a56e866a45cce8.poster.avif?t=1769591396\" width=800 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136070/extras/94451b228819058279a56e866a45cce8.webm?t=1769591396\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136070/extras/94451b228819058279a56e866a45cce8.mp4?t=1769591396\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dodge Mode</strong> – Dodge randomly generated obstacles for a unique experience every time—test your reflexes!<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136070/extras/15c0d4dcd3207b2e379249b3d1b482ab.poster.avif?t=1769591396\" width=800 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136070/extras/15c0d4dcd3207b2e379249b3d1b482ab.webm?t=1769591396\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136070/extras/15c0d4dcd3207b2e379249b3d1b482ab.mp4?t=1769591396\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Strike Mode</strong> – Sprint when the path is clear, strike or dodge when obstacles appear—balance challenge and endurance!<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136070/extras/eed8b1b885bb583ecee4d7d24fbbba31.poster.avif?t=1769591396\" width=800 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136070/extras/eed8b1b885bb583ecee4d7d24fbbba31.webm?t=1769591396\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136070/extras/eed8b1b885bb583ecee4d7d24fbbba31.mp4?t=1769591396\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🏃‍♂️Stress-Free Running:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the light-speed world of SPORTVIDA, run freely and smash through obstacles! It’s the ultimate way to relieve stress, <strong>challenging yourself while enjoying the thrill of high-speed excitement.</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136070/extras/e6511f9cc6aaf7819ea309807119a2fd.poster.avif?t=1769591396\" width=800 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136070/extras/e6511f9cc6aaf7819ea309807119a2fd.webm?t=1769591396\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136070/extras/e6511f9cc6aaf7819ea309807119a2fd.mp4?t=1769591396\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>💪Casual Fitness:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sweat it out in-game and make fitness fun! <strong>Remember to warm up before starting, grab your towel, and get ready for an exciting workout challenge!</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136070/extras/6edddd53c7878b7b2078af17af7554bb.poster.avif?t=1769591396\" width=800 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136070/extras/6edddd53c7878b7b2078af17af7554bb.webm?t=1769591396\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136070/extras/6edddd53c7878b7b2078af17af7554bb.mp4?t=1769591396\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Sportvida CyberDash</strong> is a <strong>VR running game</strong> that delivers both stress relief and thrilling challenges. Set in a high-speed, futuristic world of light and technology, you’ll embark on an intense adventure where <strong>sprinting, dodging, and smashing obstacles</strong> offer an unparalleled sense of release.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136070/extras/835277f48f4abddbb4fde8ed09b89e20.poster.avif?t=1769591396\" width=702 height=246 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136070/extras/835277f48f4abddbb4fde8ed09b89e20.webm?t=1769591396\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136070/extras/835277f48f4abddbb4fde8ed09b89e20.mp4?t=1769591396\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > In this breathtaking and luminous future world, your mission is to race to the finish line in the shortest time possible, breaking through anything that stands in your way. The game’s stunning visual effects, combined with its high-energy soundscape, immerse you in a sensation of speed and power like never before. Sportvida CyberDash is not just about exercise—it’s an exhilarating experience that lets you challenge yourself while unwinding in a fast-paced, visually stunning environment. <strong>Whether you're a fitness enthusiast or simply seeking stress relief, this game will help you find your rhythm and rediscover joy in movement.</strong>  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136070/extras/54c9436540d69b9ffa2373314cee2f5b.avif?t=1769591396\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136070/extras_big/54c9436540d69b9ffa2373314cee2f5b.avif?t=1769591396 width=800 height=125 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>💥3 Unique Game Modes</strong>:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Race Mode</strong> – Pure running with no speed limits and no obstacles—push yourself to the max and challenge your top speed!<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136070/extras/94451b228819058279a56e866a45cce8.poster.avif?t=1769591396\" width=800 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136070/extras/94451b228819058279a56e866a45cce8.webm?t=1769591396\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136070/extras/94451b228819058279a56e866a45cce8.mp4?t=1769591396\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dodge Mode</strong> – Dodge randomly generated obstacles for a unique experience every time—test your reflexes!<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136070/extras/15c0d4dcd3207b2e379249b3d1b482ab.poster.avif?t=1769591396\" width=800 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136070/extras/15c0d4dcd3207b2e379249b3d1b482ab.webm?t=1769591396\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136070/extras/15c0d4dcd3207b2e379249b3d1b482ab.mp4?t=1769591396\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Strike Mode</strong> – Sprint when the path is clear, strike or dodge when obstacles appear—balance challenge and endurance!<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136070/extras/eed8b1b885bb583ecee4d7d24fbbba31.poster.avif?t=1769591396\" width=800 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136070/extras/eed8b1b885bb583ecee4d7d24fbbba31.webm?t=1769591396\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136070/extras/eed8b1b885bb583ecee4d7d24fbbba31.mp4?t=1769591396\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🏃‍♂️Stress-Free Running:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the light-speed world of SPORTVIDA, run freely and smash through obstacles! It’s the ultimate way to relieve stress, <strong>challenging yourself while enjoying the thrill of high-speed excitement.</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136070/extras/e6511f9cc6aaf7819ea309807119a2fd.poster.avif?t=1769591396\" width=800 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136070/extras/e6511f9cc6aaf7819ea309807119a2fd.webm?t=1769591396\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136070/extras/e6511f9cc6aaf7819ea309807119a2fd.mp4?t=1769591396\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>💪Casual Fitness:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sweat it out in-game and make fitness fun! <strong>Remember to warm up before starting, grab your towel, and get ready for an exciting workout challenge!</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3136070/extras/6edddd53c78